# Admin UI

- Focus on productivity over marketing polish.
- Use robust tables (TanStack Table) and filters.
- Forms with react-hook-form + zod (if present in deps).

## Security & Access
- Enforce role-based access (RBAC) and server-side checks.
- Hide or disable UI actions when user lacks permission.

## DX
- Prefer generators for CRUD screens when possible.
- Keep routes nested by resource (e.g., /users, /orders).

## Performance
- Lazy load heavy pages (charts, reports).
